---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="HIPAA Compliance - VoiceROI" description="Learn about VoiceROI's HIPAA compliance measures for healthcare organizations using our AI Digital Workers.">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-20">
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="animate-on-scroll">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-black mb-8">HIPAA Compliance</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: January 2025</p>
            
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Healthcare Data Protection</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                VoiceROI understands the critical importance of protecting healthcare information. Our AI Digital Workers are designed with healthcare compliance in mind, ensuring that all patient data is handled according to HIPAA requirements.
              </p>
              
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Security Measures</h2>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                  <li>• End-to-end encryption for all data transmission</li>
                  <li>• Secure data storage with access controls</li>
                  <li>• Regular security audits and assessments</li>
                  <li>• Employee training on HIPAA requirements</li>
                  <li>• Business Associate Agreements (BAA) available</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Business Associate Agreement</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                For healthcare organizations, VoiceROI will execute a Business Associate Agreement (BAA) that outlines our responsibilities for protecting Protected Health Information (PHI) and ensures compliance with HIPAA regulations.
              </p>
              
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Data Handling</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Our AI Digital Workers are programmed to recognize and properly handle sensitive healthcare information. We implement appropriate safeguards to ensure that PHI is only accessed by authorized personnel and used for legitimate business purposes.
              </p>
              
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Incident Response</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                In the unlikely event of a security incident, VoiceROI has established procedures to immediately notify affected healthcare organizations and take appropriate remedial actions in accordance with HIPAA breach notification requirements.
              </p>
              
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black mb-4">Contact for Healthcare Organizations</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Healthcare organizations interested in our HIPAA-compliant AI Digital Workers should contact us to discuss specific requirements and obtain a Business Associate Agreement:
              </p>
              <div class="bg-lime-400/10 rounded-xl p-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:Hello@voiceroi.com" class="text-lime-600 hover:underline">Hello@voiceroi.com</a><br>
                  <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:646-651-4547" class="text-lime-600 hover:underline">646-651-4547</a><br>
                  <strong>Subject:</strong> HIPAA Compliance Inquiry
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>